        <div class="mb-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m0 18c-1.657 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.343-9 3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 group-hover:text-[#123472] transition-colors duration-300">
            Desarrollo Web
          </h2>
          
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Desarrollamos sitios web modernos, responsivos y optimizados con tecnologías de vanguardia, SEO avanzado y experiencias de usuario inmersivas.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-700">
            <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-[#123472] rounded-full mr-3"></div>
            <span>Frameworks modernos (React, Astro, Next.js)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-700">
            <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-[#123472] rounded-full mr-3"></div>
            <span>E-commerce y plataformas complejas</span>
